    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>paneer</strong> into bite-sized cubes</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1649782052006-x200.jpg",
